# OpenRundown (this repository)

This workspace is the **openrundown** open-source project (the MCP server and tooling), not only a consumer of the skill.

1. **Read [AGENTS.md](mdc:AGENTS.md) at the repo root** for: directory map, `project` parameter rules, `npm` commands, links to `docs/`, and how `skills/openrundown/SKILL.md` is distributed via `scripts/setup.ts`.
2. The **distributable** agent artifacts copied into other projects are: `skills/openrundown/SKILL.md`, `rules/openrundown.mdc`, and `hooks/hooks.json` — not this file. After editing the skill, run **`npm run sync:skill`** so `.cursor/skills/openrundown/SKILL.md` matches (source of truth: `skills/`).
3. For end-user product behavior, see [README.md](mdc:README.md).
